                    <comment id="12645847" author="michaelbusch" created="Fri, 7 Nov 2008 18:37:50 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Here&apos;s the patch.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;It adds the targets &apos;test-tag&apos; and &apos;clean-tags&apos;.&lt;br/&gt;
In common-build.xml I added &apos;test-macro&apos; and &apos;compile-test-macro&apos; that are shared between the standard &apos;test&apos; and new &apos;test-tag&apos; targets.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Currently all tests from Lucene 2.4 pass with trunk.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
